# ─── Python ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# ─── OS / editor ──────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
*.swp

# ─── Large dataset and GeoTIFF files ──────────────────────────
# The full Sen1Floods11 dataset stays on the cluster only.
# norm_stats.json is small and IS tracked (git add -f if needed).
data/
datasets/
*.tif
*.tiff
*.tfrecord
*.tar.gz

# ─── Model checkpoint weight files (large binaries) ───────────
# The .pt weight files are too large for GitHub (~80-100 MB each).
# config.json, eval_config.json etc. inside checkpoints/ ARE tracked.
**/*.pt

# ─── TensorBoard event files and SLURM logs ───────────────────
# Regenerable from training. Do not commit.
**/runs/

# ─── Per-chip prediction maps (many large PNGs, regenerable) ──
# Per-chip flood maps, gate maps etc. can be hundreds of files.
# Key aggregate figures (ablation_comparison.png etc.) ARE tracked.
results/eval_*/maps/
results/gate_maps_*/*_gate.png

# ─── Misc internal / secret files ─────────────────────────────
task_ids.json
run_summary.md

# ─── Tool / IDE config (not part of the project) ─────────────
.claude/
CLAUDE.md

# ─── Microsoft Office temp files ─────────────────────────────
~$*
*.tmp

# ─── Paper build artefacts (LaTeX, previews, QA images) ───────
paper/*.aux
paper/*.lof
paper/*.log
paper/*.lot
paper/*.out
paper/*.toc
paper/*_preview.pdf
paper/poster.log
paper/poster.zip
paper/pslide-*.jpg
paper/qa_*.jpg
paper/slide-*.jpg

# ─── Scratch images at repo root ──────────────────────────────
Image2.png
hand gate function*.png

# ─── Conda / pip environments ─────────────────────────────────
.conda/
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
!logs/
